表格客户主表的代码预览

drop table if exists CUST_BASEINFO;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: CUST_BASEINFO */
/*==============================================================*/
create table CUST_BASEINFO
(
CUST_CELLPHONE char(11) not null,
IDENTITY_STATUS char(1) not null default '0',
CUST_REALNAME varchar(256),
CUST_ID_CARD_NO varchar(18),
CUST_NATION varchar(20),
CUST_ADDRESS varchar(128),
CUST_ID_CARD_VAL_BEGIN date,
CUST_ID_CARD_VAL_END date,
CUST_ID_CARD_FRONT varchar(256),
CUST_ID_CARD_BACK varchar(256),
IDENTITY_TIME datetime,
IS_ENABLED bit not null default 1,
CUST_DEVICE_CODE varchar(50),
CREATE_TIME datetime not null default CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
UPDATETIME datetime not null default CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
primary key (CUST_CELLPHONE)
);
